The current blocker is that generated code is not allowed to depend on grpc++ src code for BUILD stability reasons. One possible solution is to upgrade grpc_core::CQCallbackInterface to core API (and make it C89) and then instantiate the content that uses it directly in include/grpcpp/impl/codegen . There may be other possible solutions.
